# Water Treatment Plant ER diagram

```mermaid
erDiagram
  Plant {
    string PlantId PK
    string PlantName
    string Region
  }
  Unit {
    string UnitId PK
    string UnitType
    string Status
    string PlantId FK
  }
  SensorEvent {
    string SensorEventId PK
    double FlowRateLps
    double PressureBar
    datetime Timestamp
    string UnitId FK
  }
  WaterQualitySample {
    string SampleId PK
    double TurbidityNTU
    double pH
    double ConductivityuScm
    datetime SampleTimestamp
    string PlantId FK
  }

  Plant ||--o{ Unit : operates
  Unit ||--o{ SensorEvent : hasReading
  Plant ||--o{ WaterQualitySample : sampledAt
```
